---
title: Oven-Baked Chicken Pesto Risotto Verde and Asparagus with Marinated Charred Courgette and Cheese
description: Love risottos, but wish there was no stirring involved? This Oven-Baked Pesto Risotto Verde and Asparagus is a simplified version of the traditional risotto, baking in the oven instead to absorb all the stock and flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R43_W39_UK_V19694-4_Main__5low-b0de0357.jpg
